video.title: I Made This Crazy Clock!
video.description:
To sign up for the event, just submit a brief presentation of your project.
Learn more on the website: event.3d.ru

Check out Ander's Channel: https://www.youtube.com/c/FlokrollProjects 

Download the plans for many of my projects  here: https://www.alch.shop/ 

If you want you can support me on Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/chappel  

Follow me on Instagram for more pictures and stories along the way: https://www.instagram.com/a.chappel/ 

This is the 3d printer I use:  http://shop.prusa3d.com/#a_aid=ALCH
 
Some of my favorite tools:
